{"tid":1569833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「915」不如我地Set番個目標去做，其實近期既大型活動都欠缺一個目標","createTime":"2019-09-14T18:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T06:05:48.000Z","uid":6528,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"a21ee4b494c20fe2f0bebcf6b3c13159f9dc5118","tid":1569833,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:19:06.000Z","msg":"其實香港人係輸緊俾自己<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eaHciS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eaHciS</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以睇左上面呢個Post先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n列番一啲我個人覺得比較成功既例子先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNDrPDN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNDrPDN.png&h=26577923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如有錯請話我知，我改一改。<br />\n <br />\n如果每次比較大型既活動都可以有番個目標既話，就唔需要次次都陣地戰，其實都講過好多次hit ＆ run，不過現實就係比較少發生，可能有好多因素影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，我覺得時間比較早開始進行，如7點左右，612／71／85呢三個都比起其他三個更成功，都係由朝早去到夜晚，所以其實我個人覺得愈早可能仲好，個人意見only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7d2a9e22aa0ff4c77b37805c9c7f6999d9c43e","tid":1569833,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:19:58.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f06f71f3784219e41b32a524e02e06a4a20acf","tid":1569833,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:20:58.000Z","ms