 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:26:11.000Z","msg":"聽日一定會出黎放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眼見而家好多時都好似冇一個明確既見標出黎咁，所以最後都係開個post，一齊諗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c171206204611931971dca65db5372bc776464c","tid":1569833,"uid":131125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:26:56.000Z","msg":"其實唔覺得85算係<br />\n原目標係三罷，到後面演變成地區衝突<br />\n而洗淡左原本三罷嘅效果<br />\n<br />\n另外同意搞活動真係要有目標<br />\n衰左都好最多出黎現場再轉plan(71<br />\n就算出黎充撐人頭行完就走都可以講明<br />\n咁就應該會少左好多留守嘅人(因為果班都未必知自己想點，都係見步行步/想留後保護和理非)<br />\n目標明確就唔會咁多位分化到(好似817臥底狗根本引唔到人去狗屋，因為果日大家有明確目標唔好起衝突，留返造就818和平集會)"},{"pid":"2b1e2ecd927e30e4ab21ab834e5e237080f0d36b","tid":1569833,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"90f96843975b2786aab7015e4378fc123901b46f","tid":1569833,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:27:22.000Z","msg":"針對翻警察濫權 濫捕 選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c56c1942b6676fd1e28d3a111473f34402535622","tid":1569833,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb5c69a18254c7e10e04a6b1b55d3af3d09ec52","tid":1569833,"uid":97716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:28:08.000Z","msg":"講真我完全唔知聽日出去的目的係咩<br />\n次次都係叫一大班人出去<br />\n企 set rb 之後等狗到<br />\n有tg就後退 <br />\n之後和理非走 狗向前拉人 冇人去救<br />\n散唔到場 因為會