"2019-09-14T19:04:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85b97fe6b0340403db9328c0639b701eaa853d09","tid":1569833,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feaed4a882d22b540b3f7c7b2fcb8046b878a0f7","tid":1569833,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a5c407e09c9bda074c0c93ffc6f0a285892c04a","tid":1569833,"uid":156679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6607c6389f36dc46c8d8d884d25e9fcfc34f6942","tid":1569833,"uid":228888,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:53:39.000Z","msg":"唔講目標 講時間囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">例如：大家一齊幾點一齊走</span></span><br />\n次次散場都係<br />\n有好多人個心態係 見人地未走我又唔走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解次次都係散場拉得最多？<br />\n因為佢見小人 啲人又唔肯走！<br />\n<br />\n大家定一個時間 到個個鐘數就一次過<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Be water</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n例如 9點 <br />\n大家8點個時一齊提 <br />\n重有一個鐘就散<br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n8點半 再提<br />\n半個鐘 揾好點翻屋企未<br />\n<br />\n次次出黎大家都無共識幾點走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T18:57:20.000Z","msg":"同意 齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:05:21.000Z","msg":"你要約埋一齊走先肯走<br />\n咁有人要留或者有卧底呃你地留咪又係有人跟住留<br />\n<br />\n點解決？<br />\n我建議就係要用返樓主quote個post講嗰樣野<br />\n問自己<br />\n「每次出黎嘅目的係乜先？」<br />\n達成目的咪完左當日嘅任務返屋企休息<br />\n<br />\n如果當日出黎根本搵唔到點先為之達成目的<br />\nEnd up就會係我地見慣嘅set rb/俾狗圍/逃亡呢啲<br />\n咁就要諗下點解個活動會冇目的同埋睇下點進步"},{"pid":"e5945204bdce56e7a4678b34ba0e62b5d4c91891","tid":1569833,"uid":203926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T20:23:15.000Z","msg":"有不反對就遊行 有衝突就勇武保護和理非走先<br />\n冇不反對就行街 幫襯黃店 逼死藍店 痴滿文宣<br />\n依家問題係大家可以出完嚟第二日照常返工<br />\n喺要維持平日照常運作既情況下好難再升級<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12cfefe397d540bd712645abccd8c282f53823c","tid":1569833,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T00:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebcbcac7989641222a37ad583e09b4a03aaa3b7","tid":1569833,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6fa14c8fe35cf4b6f46fdd6be3bf68410fa0f6","tid":1569833,"uid":237528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:19:40.000Z","msg":"今日9.15 大遊行<br />\n希望勇武堅持「不受傷 不被捕」既原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好死守 等狗衝<br />\n<br />\n依家被狗捉左 唔係係狗屋坐48小時咁簡單<br />\n係直接送去新屋嶺被狗打殘，強姦，被自殺，肢解，活摘器官，送番大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企人要被迫滅聲<br />\n女義士救下你地唔好行咁前 班狗專捉女性<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完左個遊行<br />\n請大家要留意身邊有冇秘密警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時間最好換左衫先搭車<br />\n留意商場既監控鏡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己個人覺得全黑已經無必要<br />\n全黑最大既好處係保護身邊既同路人<br />\n但對家有臥底警察 所以都係要獨立思考<br />\n而全黑最大既壞處係好容易被秘密警察係回家既路上伏擊<br />\n不過 尊重大家決定 依然全黑去遊行<br />\n<br />\n希望大家遊行完之後繼續提高警覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a42ef29147b75325aaf15451cd541927d536e3","tid":1569833,"uid":92188,"li